      "comment": "SOKAI (1) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at six of 16 starts including six wins but missed the frame latest when fourth (22.89) over 395m at Murray Bridge. Has never missed the frame at the trip from six starts. Drawn the rails and rates a key runner. CHIVAS LADY (2) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from five tries. Comes off a (17.71) win last time, scoring by a neck in a TG1-4W over 305m at Mt Gambier. Looks suited here and can measure up. COMPTON STELLA (8) is having her first look at this course. Scored in one of the quickest times on the card (23.16) latest, winning by 4.5 lengths at Mt Gambier in a Grade 6. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Significant danger. GOLDIE RUSTY (4) is sure to play a big role again after a run of minor placings.",
